OL,4,Cand pence format to end 'nasty
OL,5,Csurprises'
OL,7,FHousehold telecoms bills must now set
OL,8,Fout contract price rises in pounds and
OL,9,Fpence to prevent the "nasty surprises"
OL,10,Fof inflation-based hikes.
OL,12,FPhone, broadband and pay TV providers
OL,13,Fare now banned from linking price
OL,14,Frises to future rates of inflation,
OL,15,Fwhich often include an extra
OL,16,Fpercentage increase on top, and which
OL,17,Fmade it near impossible for consumers
OL,18,Fto accurately estimate what they would
OL,19,Fpay.
