OL,5,Csurprises'
OL,7,FIt also complicated the process of
OL,8,Fcomparing firms when shopping around
OL,9,Ffor a new deal.
OL,11,FNow, firms must set out any future
OL,12,Fprice hikes "prominently and
OL,13,Ftransparently" in pounds and pence at
OL,14,Fthe point of sale.
OL,16,FThis means consumers will be able to
OL,17,Fchoose a contract featuring
OL,18,Finformation in pounds and pence ahead
OL,19,Fof annual price rises in April.
