OL,7,FHowever, while the new rules ban
OL,8,Finflation-linked price rises, they
OL,9,Fstill allow for annual mid-contract
OL,10,Fincreases by a fixed amount.
OL,12,FLast April many deals rose by 7.7%, in
OL,13,Fline with the Consumer Price Index
OL,14,Fannounced in February as 4% plus an
OL,15,Fadditional 3.9%.
OL,17,FOther deals rose by up to 8.8% in line
OL,18,Fwith the Retail Price Index, which was
OL,19,F4.9%, plus 3.9%.
