OL,3,CTelecoms bills must now be in pounds
OL,4,Cand pence format to end 'nasty
OL,5,Csurprises'
OL,7,FOfcom said: "As we have seen in recent
OL,8,Fyears, inflation can be incredibly
OL,9,Fvolatile and is difficult to predict.
OL,11,F"Our rules will protect consumers from
OL,12,Fbearing that risk, and ensure
OL,13,Fproviders are clear about prices
OL,14,Fcustomers are obliged to pay over the
OL,15,Fwhole contract period."
OL,17,FAny price rises written into a
OL,18,Fcustomer's contract also now need to
OL,19,Fbe set out "prominently and
OL,20,Ftransparently", at the point of sale.
