OL,7,FProviders must also be clear about
OL,8,Fwhenany changes to prices will occur.
OL,10,FNatalie Black, Ofcom's group director
OL,11,Ffor networks and communications, said:
OL,12,F"More than ever, households want and
OL,13,Fneed to plan their budgets.
OL,15,F"Our new rules mean there will be no
OL,16,Fnasty surprises, and customers will
OL,17,Fknow how much they will be paying and
OL,18,Fwhen, through clear labelling."
