OL,7,FHe said: "Many providers have now
OL,8,Fopted for a blanket flat-rate annual
OL,9,Fprice rise that will be even higher
OL,10,Fthan the inflation-linked approach for
OL,11,Fthe average broadband customer.
OL,13,F"So if you're on a cheaper or average-
OL,14,Fpriced contract, the luxury of knowing
OL,15,Fwhat your exact price rise is in
OL,16,Fadvance comes at the cost of an even
OL,17,Fsteeper bill hike ` effectively a
OL,18,F'transparency tax' for consumers."
